quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  34,46,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko mi waajorta on, ko (huunde) wootere: \"Ko nde daroranton Alla …ói…óo …ói…óo e gooto gooto, refti miijito…óon. (Anndon) wondii…óo mon on aldaa e jinna: O wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo on, e ko woni yeeso (mon), e lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  34,47,"Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njo…ìdi, …óum ko fii mon. Njo…ìdi am ndin wonaali, si wanaa ka Alla. Kanko Ko O Seedii…óo e kala huunde"
  34,48,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am ko werlortoo…óo [meere nden, hujjaaji] goonga kan, timmin…óo anndugol wirnii…ói"
  34,49,"Maaku: \"Goonga kan arii [Iislaamu on], meere [keeferaaku] ngun alaa ka fee√±a, kadi, nde ruttotaako"
  34,50,"Maaku: \"Si mi majjii, haray ko hoore-am mi majjani; si mi feewii kadi, ko sabu ko sabu ko Joomi am wahayini e am kon, tawde pellet, ko O Nanoowo, ∆Åadii…óo"
  34,51,"Sinno a tinayno, tuma nde …ìe …óenyii, - laaworde alanaa (…ìe), - …ìe nanngiree e nokkuure …ìadiinde"
  34,52,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii [Darngal] ngal\", e ko honno gom…óinal woonirani …ìe e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo"
  34,53,"Hara non …ìe yeddiino nde ko adii, hi…ìe werlora ko wirnii e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo"
  34,54,"Heedee hakkunde e ko …ìe tuuyetee, wano golliranoo e nanndo ma…ì…ìe ko adii, tawde …ìe woniino e sikke cikkinii…óa"
  35,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, Tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, Wa…óu…óo Malaa'ika'en nulaa…ìe, mar…ìe gabitanji(bibje) …ói …ói…ói, …ói tati e nayi. Himo …ìeyda ko O muuyi e tagu Makko ngun, tawde pellet, Alla ko hattan…óo kala huunde"
  35,2,"Kala yurmeende nde Alla udditani yim…ìe …ìen, jogitotoo…óo nde alaa; kala kadi ko O jogitii, accitoowo …óum alaa …ìaawo (jogitagol) Makko. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  35,3,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe! jantee neema Alla on e mon. Hara tagoowo ko woori Alla no woodi, mo no arsikira on ka kammu e ka leydi? Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Kanko! E ko honno yiilirte…óon [e kaa goonga]"
  35,4,"Si …ìe fennii ma, pellet Nulaa…ìe (goo) fennanooma ado maa. Ko faade e Alla, woni ruttorde fiyakuuji …óin"
  35,5,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe! Anndee pellet fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wata nguurndam aduna hodu on, wata (seytaane) hodoowo on hodu on e fii Alla"
  35,6,"Pellet, seytaane ko ga√±o wonani on. Haray jogitoree mo ga√±o. Anndee ko o noddirta fedde makko nden, ko no …ìe jeydiree e yim…ìe dul…ìoowe ngen"
  35,7,"Hino woodani yeddu…ìe …ìen, lepte sa…ótu…óe. ∆Åeya gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, hino woodani …ìe haforaneede e njo…ìdi mawndi"
  35,8,"E ko on cu…óinanaa…óo golle mun bon…óe, hara himo yi'a …óe mo∆¥∆¥u…óe? - Tawde pellet, Alla no majjina on Mo O muuyi, O fewna Mo O muuyi. Wata a tampinir hoore-maa, sunagol fii ma…ì…ìe. Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo ko …ìe woni huuwude"
  35,9,"Ko Alla woni wurtu…óo keneeli …óin, …ói sogga duule, Men yarnira …óum leydi yoorundi; Men wuurnitira …óum leydi ndin, …ìaawo ndi yoorude. Ko wano non ummital ngal"
  35,10,"Kala taw…óo ko teddungal faalaa (yo o …óa…ì…ìir Alla), tawde ko Alla jeyi teddungal ngal fow: ko ka Makko woni ko konngol laa…ìungol ∆¥awata, golle mo∆¥∆¥e …óen …ìamta ngol. ∆Åen fewjoo…ìe boneeji, hino woodani …ìe lepte sa…ótu…óe. Pewje …ìen …óen, ko bonay …óe"
  35,11,"Ko Alla tagiri on e mbulbuldi, refti e to…ì…ìere (maniiyu), refti O wa…ói on nooneeji. Deyel saawataa, ngel lelnataa kadi, si wanaa e anndal Makko. Wuurnaa…óo wuurnetaake, …óuytetaake kadi e nguurndam makko, si wanaa no e deftere. Pellet, …óum ko newanii …óum Alla"
  35,12,"Maaje …óen …ói…ói fotataa: [Ndiyam] goo …óoo …óam, ko wel…óam, laa…ìungo, newiingo njaram mun, ngoo …óaa, ko lan…óam haa…óu…óam. Hi…óon √±aama e kala majjam, teewu keccu, hi…óon yaltina kadi hen, cu…óaari ndi …ìoornoto…óon. Hi…óa yi'a laa…óe …óen no awja e maggo, fii yo on …óa…ì…ìiron e …ìural Makko. Belajoo on yettay [Mo]"
  35,13,"Himo naada jemma on e der √±alorma on, O naada √±alorma on e nder jemma on. O elti kadi naange ngen e lewru ndun. Kala mun no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Ko On moo…óon woni Alla, Joomi mon: Ko Kanko Laamu woodani. ∆äiya …ói noddoton gaanin Makko, …ói jeytaa yeru gorol tamara"
  35,14,"Si on noddu …ói, …ói nanataa noddaandu mon; hay si …ói nanoy, …ói jaabitotaako on. √ëalnde Darngal, …ói yeddoyay sirku mon on. Alaa habroowo ma, wano Humpitii…óo On"